data.description: Beautiful first floor 2 bed 2 bath condo in the heart of Schaumburg. Located near the expressway along with restaurants, shopping centers, and conveniences galore. Kitchen boasts extended breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Extra dining area right off the living room for larger gatherings or extra space.  The living room is bright and full of sun thanks to the custom vertical blinds.  Huge master bedroom and bathroom with a giant walk in closet with plenty of storage.  Laundry room located on the second floor.  Park your car right in front of your patio doors. Plenty of visitor parking. Schedule your private showing today!
